title: The Honest Company Foaming Bubble Bath | Gentle for Baby | Naturally Derived, Tear-free, Hypoallergenic | Lavender Calm, 12 fl oz
description: From mama’s self-care to baby’s bathtime routine, this tear-free, super-foaming bubble bath is the perfect way to wind down. Made with chamomile extract, aloe and other naturally derived ingredients, this lavender-scented, gentle-for-baby fam-fave brings all the calming vibes.
